{"type": "article", "id": 26857, "title": "节水手提袋", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-16T06:45:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 52, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021324532tUbeD16QzYW3TEh.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>为了等洗澡水变热而浪费的水平均有 3-6 升，这个生活中的小细节启发了来自西班牙的团队 <a href=\"http://esferic.com/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">esferic</a>，设计出了这款名为 WaterDrop 的手提袋。他们还专门为希望参与节水行动的孩子们设计了一款儿童版手提袋，可以装下 1.5 升的水。esferic 还推出了配套的手机应用，它不仅可以记录你每天的节水量，还会告诉你所有 WaterDrop 的使用者一共节约了多少水，体现了节水社区的概念。WaterDrop 目前还在 <a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/waterdrop-don-t-waste-water#/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Indiegogo</a> 上进行众筹，最低售价为 12 欧元一只。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132448Oo7QGbVJ2RTFhsad.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132449rTyiBplEF16CWYsQ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070213245004HT5MUb6QBdF9Vu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67152104\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132451zghXlkbU6WRqwC5J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6763285\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132451qFcYjma3rbDiP7XG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69032258\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132451SrgYn7w3yplmoNKj.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n\n\n"}